    "revelation": "Tape saturation is not distortion — it is a material property, a physical memory of every note that has passed through it.",
    "diagnosis": "Acetate Mono isolates the tape character: analog drift at its highest, drive near maximum, sending zero signal to reverb. The decay of this sound is the decay of the medium."
